title: 07/30/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 07/30/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps yesterday's NBA Draft and trades with Chris Mannix. Fresh off Team USA Women's Soccer win over the Netherlands in Penalty Kicks, Goalkeeper Alyssa Naeher joins us from Tokyo to recap the match. And ESPN's Dan Orlovsky explains why Jets fans should temper their expectations.
